    <item>
      <title>Uber 将在纽约司机中途停职，以降低最低工资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/uber-is-locking-out-new-york-city-drivers-mid-shift-to-lower-minimum-pay</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了对抗最低工资规定，Uber Technologies Inc. 已开始在需求低迷时期禁止纽约市司机使用其应用，Lyft Inc. 也威胁要采取同样的措施。结果，一些司机表示他们的工资下降了 50%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/uber-is-locking-out-new-york-city-drivers-mid-shift-to-lower-minimum-pay</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 17:17:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
